snippet.title: theHunter Classic  |  Community Creators!  | Trailer by Nuubialainen
snippet.description:
The winning trailer of theHunter community competition in May 2014.

Credits:
Author: Community member Nuubialainen
Actors: Community members Killertut, Andrewfreeman, TurkSDSU, mateusz473, tim1212xd, Rennsemmel, Triskeleton, Kizzzaa, Randel18, Vihreesavi

Music: Epic Song, by BoxCat Games.
http://freemusicarchive.org/music/BoxCa ... _Epic_Song
The gunshots and animal noises were added, and are not originally part of the song. (This information is provided due to Creative Commons Attribution license, which requires mentioning if anything is changed in the original content.)
